---
---

<section id="services" class="services" aria-labelledby="services-heading">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">What we do</p>
    <h2 id="services-heading">Formwork services</h2>
    <p class="section-lede">
      Traditional and system formwork for residential, commercial and civil concrete work.
    </p>

    <ul class="card-grid" role="list">
      <li class="card">
        <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="28" height="28">
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M4 26h6v-4h6v-4h6v-4h6v-4h4v18H4z" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Concrete stairs</h3>
        <p>
          Cast in-situ staircases — straight flights, dog-legs and helical — formed cleanly, set
          true, finished to a high standard.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="28" height="28">
            <path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M4 6h24v4H4zm0 6h24v4H4zm0 6h24v4H4zm0 6h24v4H4z"
              opacity=".4"
            />
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M6 4v24h2V4zm18 0v24h2V4z" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Walls &amp; retaining walls</h3>
        <p>
          Plumb, tight, well-tied wall forms for basements, retaining structures and feature
          concrete finishes.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="28" height="28">
            <path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M3 16h26v3H3zm2 5h22v3H5zm-2-9 13-7 13 7v2H3z"
            />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Slabs &amp; foundations</h3>
        <p>
          Suspended slabs, ground bearing slabs, pile caps and foundations — set out accurately and
          poured cleanly.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="28" height="28">
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M12 4h8v24h-8zM6 8h4v20H6zm16 0h4v20h-4z" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Columns</h3>
        <p>
          Square, rectangular and circular columns — properly braced forms with crisp arrises and a
          clean fair-faced finish where needed.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="28" height="28">
            <path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M4 4h24v4H4zm0 8h24v4H4zm0 8h24v4H4zM8 4v24h2V4zm14 0v24h2V4z"
            />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>Reinforced concrete structures</h3>
        <p>
          Frames, cores and decks — coordinated with the steel fixers and concrete gangs to keep
          the programme moving.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="card">
        <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" width="28" height="28">
            <path
              fill="currentColor"
              d="M4 6h12v12H4zm14 0h10v8H18zm0 10h10v12H18zM4 20h12v8H4z"
            />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <h3>System &amp; traditional formwork</h3>
        <p>
          Comfortable on both modular system kit and bespoke timber formwork — whichever suits the
          job and the finish required.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
